  "prompt": "Who is the best Batman actor in your opinion?",
  "response": "As an AI, I don't have personal opinions. However, I can share that the best Batman actor is a matter of personal preference and can vary depending on who you ask. Some of the most popular actors who have portrayed Batman include:\n\n1. **Michael Keaton** - Known for his role in Tim Burton's \"Batman\" (1989) and \"Batman Returns\" (1992), Keaton's performance is often praised for its balance of intensity and charm.\n   \n2. **Christian Bale** - His portrayal in Christopher Nolan's \"The Dark Knight\" trilogy (2005-2012) is widely acclaimed for its depth and realism.\n\n3. **Ben Affleck** - Affleck brought a more seasoned and weary Batman to life in the DC Extended Universe films, starting with \"Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice\" (2016).\n\n4. **Robert Pattinson** - Pattinson's performance in \"The Batman\" (2022) has been well-received for its fresh and gritty take on the character.\n\nUltimately, the \"best\" Batman actor can vary based on individual taste and the aspects of the character that resonate most with different viewers.",
